                        "lang" : "java",
                        "type" : "code",
                        "value" : "Dog fido = new Dog();\n DogLover john = new DogLover()\n john.dogs.add(fido);\n john.dogs.add(fido);\n assert john.dogs.size() == 2;\n assert fido.owners.size() == 2;\n "
